    dcterms:description "Voice & Tone sweep: Read aloud to hear inconsistencies. Mark tone shifts. Smooth transitions. Return to Clarity to verify no confusion introduced." ;
    oc:expectedOutcome "Consistent formality and brand personality throughout" ;
